title: HP ENVY Black Curved All-In-One Desktop Computer 34-A010 - Overview
description:
HP ENVY Black Curved All-In-One Desktop Computer - M9Z77AAABA http://www.abt.com/product/95802/HP-M9Z77AAABA.html

Specifications:
• Operating System: Windows 10 Home
• Processor
o 6th generation Intel Core™ i5-6400T
o Quad-Core
• Processor Speed: 2.20GHz
• Turbo Boost: 2.80GHz
• Cache: 6MB Cache
• Memory: 12GB DDR4-2133 SDRAM memory 1x8GB and 1x4GB (expandable to 16 GB; 2x 8GB)
• Hard Drive: 1TB 5400RPM Serial ATA hard drive
• Video Graphics
o NVIDIA GeForce 960A graphics card with 2GB GDDR5 dedicated memory
o Up to 8122MB Total Available Graphics Memory as allocated by Windows 10 Network
• Interface: 10/100/1000 Base-T Network
• Wireless Connectivity: Integrated Bluetooth 4.0 and Wireless LAN 802.11a/b/g/n/ac featuring Dual-band (2.4GHz and 5GHz) 2x2 technology
• Sound
o Integrated speakers
o Bang & Olufsen
• Memory Slots: 2 DDR4 DIMM (SODIMM) (occupied)
• Expansion Slots: 2 M.2 (one available)
• Memory Card Reader: HP 3-in-1 Media Card Reader–Supports SD SDHC SDXC
• External Ports
o Headphone/Microphone Combo
o HDMI Out
o Rear I/O: 2 x USB 3.0 3 x USB 2.0
o Bottom: 2 x USB 3.0
• Mouse and Keyboard: Black and white wireless chiclet-style keyboard with volume control and black and white optical mouse
• Web Camera: Intel RealSense™ 3D Camera (1920 x 1080 2 MP) with integrated dual microphones; infrared (640 x 480) camera
• Integrated Display
o 34 curved diagonal widescreen IPS Quad HD+ LED backlit edge-to-edge display (3440x1440)
o Technicolor Color Certified Display
• Display Resolution: 3440x1440 (Quad HD+)
• Tilt/Stand Design
o Tilt Angle: 0 to 25
o Stand Type: Cantilever
• Power Supply: 180W Power Supply (external)
